{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-03223/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-03223"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["0:32:23"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Creator"]},"value":{"none":["Paul Thomas Anderson"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["full shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["eye-level"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["mobile, tracking, crane, tilt"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["group shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A man and woman enter a restaurant, and the man hands their coats to the host."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03223/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-03223","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03223/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-03223"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03223/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03223/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03223/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03223/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03223/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03223/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03223/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03223/canvas/1/18748fec-e685-41d5-a2d4-838b5f826382","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T14:00:36.301Z","creator":"g","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>The bright green of the bar, a color that comes to be associated with Alma, stands out against the darker neutrals of the rest of the frame. Reynolds has brought Alma with him to the city, and her presence brings new color to his life. It is almost as if she has brought the green of the hills from the previous scene with her, bringing the natural world into his life.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03223/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:118.05825242718444,625.4368932038835,427.1844660194174,306.0194174757281"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03223/canvas/1/8d949899-5711-4051-975c-8fffd25d9877","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T14:00:47.350Z","creator":"g","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>In an elision facilitated by editing, we have now skipped over the time required by Reynolds to craft this dress. The music swells as Reynolds and Alma enter the restaurant, marking her debut into society at Reynolds’s level.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03223/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:764.2718446601941,342.71844660194176,276.50485436893223,507.96116504854365"}}}]}]}]}